-----------------------------------------------------------------

    POLCHAT   A polarisation-consistent charge-fitting tool
              A Molecolab tool

-----------------------------------------------------------------


About POLCHAT
-------------------------
  POLCHAT is a tool developed by the Molecolab group at the
    Department of Chemistry, University of Pisa, Italy.
  For the other Molecolab tools please visit the website
    www.dcci.unipi.it/molecolab/tools.

  POLCHAT is written in fortran90. It derives atomic partial
    charges, in the MK scheme, consistent with atomic 
    polarisations in the induced-dipole approach. Different
    interaction models are available (see documentation).

