Documentation
-------------------------
  The main documentation for POLCHAT usage is in doc/polchat.pdf.
  There is also a limited help for commands:
    polchat.exe -h

Compilation & Testing
-------------------------
  POLCHAT can be compiled by running 'make' in /src.
  Examples with input and output can be found in /examples and
    can be used for testing.

